## Migration Path from Current Architecture

| Current | New | Change |
|---------|-----|--------|
| `AgentHandler.query()` | `AgentAdapter.startTurn()` + `AgentAdapter.steerTurn()` | Split fire-and-forget query into explicit turn start + multi-turn steer |
| `AgentHandler.cancel()` | `AgentAdapter.interruptTurn()` | Add turnId parameter for precision |
| `AgentHandler.reset()` | `AgentAdapter.stopThread()` | Rename + thread-scoped |
| `AgentHandler.initialize()` | `AgentAdapter.initialize()` | Same |
| `SessionState` in-memory maps | `Thread` + `Turn` DB-backed | Persist turn history for rollback/fork |
| `FrontendClient.sendMessage()` | `AgentEvent` stream | Decouple adapter from transport |
| `saveUserMessage()` in sidecar | Move to server layer | Adapter shouldn't do DB writes |
| `protocol.ts` Zod schemas | Shared typed event schemas | Same approach, expanded event types |

